        <updateDate>2017-10-24T21:45:16Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Same Day Registration Act</b></p> <p> This bill amends the Help America Vote Act of 2002 to require states with a voter registration requirement to make same-day voter registration available at the polling place on any day voting is permitted.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
